comments.html:
I find myself here, once again, at the tree. Comfort finds me under it, yet I fear my words are being rewritten. Bathed in purple and under its branches, I cannot speak with the capitalisation for which I am so attached.

I find every press of the shift key useless. I reach for the caps lock key only to find it inert. screams echo out from within the trunk. the tree‚Äôs branches sway in the wind. ‚Äúplease help me,‚Äù I hear myself call, ‚ÄúSave me from this fate.‚Äù

Return of the capitalisation

Sorry to have troubled you friend, but I have good news, there's a button in the settings dialog for toggling capitalisation!
